resources.string:
There are five buttons and one slider to control the car. 
The four buttons with arrow symbols are used to control the direction of your vehicle. 
The stop button in the center can be used to immediately stop the vehicle. 
The slider on the right can be used to control the speed of the vehicle. 
We hope that you have a lot of fun in the Esstelleague!
